<p>1. The 50% Sports Welcome Bonus up to &euro;75 or currency equivalent is available to ArtemisBet customers that have not yet placed a bet in the sportsbook.</p>
<p>2. The bonus is shown on the deposit page.&nbsp;By selecting this bonus and making a deposit of at least &euro;10 or currency equivalent, the customer will instantly receive a 50% bonus up to &euro;75 or currency equivalent.</p>
<p>3. In the rare event that a deposit bonus is not automatically granted after selecting the bonus on the deposit page and making a qualifying deposit, please contact Customer Support by email or Live Chat as soon as possible, before placing any bets and our staff will manually grant the bonus;</p>
<p>4. Both the qualifying deposit amount and the granted bonus amount will be held as bonus funds until the bonus wagering requirement has been met;</p>
<p>5. The total amount held as bonus funds must be wagered 15 times (15x) with all bets settled, before the bonus funds and qualifying deposit amount are released to the customer's real money balance.</p>
<p>Example: customer makes deposit of &euro;150 and receives the full bonus amount of &euro;75. Qualifying deposit amount of &euro;150 + bonus funds of &euro;75 = &euro;225. &euro;225 must be wagered 15 times (15x) before the bonus funds and qualifying deposit amount are released to the customer&rsquo;s real money balance</p>
<p>For the following countries, the wagering requirement is 20 times (20x): Armenia, Australia, Belarus, Croatia, Cyprus, Greece, Hungary, Lithuania, Montenegro, Portugal, Poland, Russia,  Slovenia, Ukraine and the United Kingdom.</p>
<p>6. This bonus is not currently available to customers from Serbia and Bulgaria;</p>
<p>7.&nbsp;The wagering requirement must be met within 30 days of the customer's qualifying deposit.</p>
<p>8. The customer has the right to cancel this bonus at any time by contacting Customer Support by email or Live Chat. In the case of a net loss of bonus balance, this loss will be deducted from the qualifying deposit amount and only the remaining balance will be added to the customer&rsquo;s real money balance;</p>
<p>9. Only bets with odds 2.0 or higher are permitted while betting to meet the wagering requirement;</p>
<p>10. When placing bets with the bonus funds, only up to a maximum of &euro;50, or currency equivalent, will count towards the wagering requirement per bet;</p>
<p>11. The following betting type is excluded when bets are placed with the bonus funds: <em>Outrights;</em></p>
<p>12. ArtemisBet reserves the right to cancel this promotion or to change the terms and conditions of this promotion at any time and it is the customer's responsibility to periodically check this page for changes and updates;</p>
<p>13. <a href="https://m.artemisbet.com/sports/sportsbonusterms">General Terms for Sports Bonuses</a> also apply.</p>
